Project structure

qa_ai_bot/
├── main.py                         # Entry point to start the Telegram bot
├── .env                            # API keys (Google + Telegram), ignored by Git
├── requirements.txt                # Python dependencies
│
├── handlers/
│   ├── messages.py                 # Handles incoming user prompts
│   └── callbacks.py                # Handles button clicks (doc type selection)
│
├── ai/
│   └── doc_generator.py            # Sends prompt + doc type to Gemini and returns output

